10,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"各有各做法<br />\n就算唔認同其他人做法, 都唔好咁仆街割蓆同篤灰<br />\n你驚有事, 你可以沉默<br />\n<br />\n做法想法唔同, 但大家目標都係反條例<br />\n唔好咁仆街割蓆同篤灰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"不篤灰,不割蓆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不和理非</span></span>"},{"pid":"93f9f0ae631d42d642e91bb1cff7d87a790ce775","tid":1199951,"uid":162866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"帶<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">電筒</span></span></strong>！！"},{"pid":"f14a31edc4e519f9bd9c5f2e2b209f0a716c3da0","tid":1199951,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"有人用棍拍野deam beat 既時候唔好劣<br />\n一齊叫同一句口號加士氣避免士氣此消彼長<br />\n有心理學背後原理<br />\n對陣口號可參考港隊打氣口號<br />\n拍拍~拍拍拍~DIE FOR HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n另外大家小心雙眼，戴眼罩被人噴油漆就喪失視力，唔戴又會比人插眼<br />\n<br />\n大家亦小心近距離突然由下巴向上大力推有機會導致頸椎受傷 請各位注意安全免生危險"},{"pid":"8506b9180a10324ab2cb6118b4581a3b1cc4ff3a","tid":1199951,"uid":145758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:11:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a3ce6733a65b8f7ab93d9487b8fc9b1817e90cd","tid":1199951,"uid":48571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c656c831e04c8e6b3f36345dca3bb6d3f951316f","tid":1199951,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:12:23.000Z","msg":"[想衝但又怕嘅入嚟] 各種分工 衝要用腦有陣形<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1200053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1200053</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4ae2483ddec87460eb9b9bb48451efb93f0a6f2","tid":1199951,"uid":32352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:12:25.000Z","msg":"要用遠攻 不宜近攻<br />\n保持距離"},{"pid":"41d8f0f8ce70324226355590ef92f366ea38c3fd","tid":1199951,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b91350c2a1901e